  <brief_title>Safety Study of Dexmedetomidine in Septic Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effective Dose of Dexmedetomidine for Moderate Sedation of Adult Intubated Septic Patients in the ICU.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
